>> time required: 1 hours
>> course: sauce

Deed seed about half of @habenero peppers{20-25}
Add to a pot the habeneros, @pineapple{1%cup}, @peach{1}, juice of @lime{1}, and @banana{1}
Add @white vinegar{1.5%cups}, @salt{1.5%tsp}, @water{.5%cup}, and @sugar{1%tbsp}
Bring to a boil and simmer ~{15%minutes},
Add @olive oil{2%tbsp}
Blend in blender then refine through a tamis
Bottle.
